Package: nonprobcover
Title: Coverage Simulations for the nonprobsvy Package
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Maciej", "Beresewicz", email = "maciej.beresewicz@ue.poznan.pl",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Internal helper package for running Monte Carlo coverage
    simulations of estimators implemented in the nonprobsvy package.
    Provides a YAML-driven driver, data-generating processes from the
    methods literature, coverage metrics, and CSV writers used by the
    coverage-verification website.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
